  ‚ü®/- This is defeq to `map‚āā (-ŠĶ•) f g`, but the hypothesis unfolds to `t‚āĀ -ŠĶ• t‚āā ‚äÜ s` rather than all
  the way to `Set.image2 (-ŠĶ•) t‚āĀ t‚āā ‚äÜ s`. -/
  fun f g => { map‚āā (¬∑ -ŠĶ• ¬∑) f g with sets := { s | ‚ąÉ t‚āĀ ‚ąą f, ‚ąÉ t‚āā ‚ąą g, t‚āĀ -ŠĶ• t‚āā ‚äÜ s } }‚ü©

scoped[Pointwise] attribute [instance] Filter.instVSub

@[simp]
